
Eclipse JEE
Change prespective to JEE
Go to Server tab
Add Tomcat Server -> Specify Tomcat Directory
Dobule click on tomcat entry under Server tab
Change Server location to "Use Tomcat Installation"
Start Server
check if Tomcat is running

New -> Dynamic WEb Project -> Tick on Generate Deployment descriptor (Checkbox)
Right click project and add JSP
Right click project -> Run On Server

